<p>When you&#8217;re A-OK with these things, it&#8217;s time to get into the beefy stuff. Let&#8217;s just get right to it.</p>
<div class="woo-sc-box tick   ">By finishing this page, you should be good with all the possible conversions for passive form. Now you&#8217;re ready to learn how the grammar part of passive form works</div>
